---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Container } from "@/components/layout/Container";
---

<Layout
    title="Daycare Marketing Strategies | Childcare Business Plan"
    description="Discover effective daycare marketing strategies tailored to your local market competition and saturation levels."
>
    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section class="py-12 md:py-20">
        <Container size="md">
            <div class="text-center mb-8 md:mb-12">
                <span
                    class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 text-xs font-semibold mb-3"
                >
                    Growth Strategy
                </span>
                <h1
                    class="text-2xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 md:mb-6"
                >
                    YOUR Enrollment Growth
                </h1>
                <p class="text-base md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    True growth comes from understanding that your center is a
                    unique brand in your community, not just another option on
                    the list.
                </p>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>

    <!-- FACTORS SECTION -->
    <section class="py-8 md:py-16">
        <Container size="md">
            <div
                class="glass-panel rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-10 mb-6 md:mb-8"
            >
                <h2
                    class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 md:mb-6"
                >
                    What Affects Your Marketing Success
                </h2>
                <div
                    class="space-y-4 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed"
                >
                    <p>
                        Your ability to fill spots depends heavily on local
                        market saturation, the specific demographics of families
                        in your radius, and the intensity of competition nearby.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        What works in a dense urban center will fail in a
                        suburban setting. Your marketing approach must match
                        your market reality.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>

    <!-- WHY GENERIC FAILS SECTION -->
    <section class="py-8 md:py-16">
        <Container size="md">
            <div class="glass-panel rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-10">
                <h2
                    class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 md:mb-6"
                >
                    Why Online Advice Often Conflicts
                </h2>
                <div
                    class="space-y-4 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed"
                >
                    <p>
                        Marketing gurus often push expensive digital ads that
                        may not reach your specific local parents.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Your marketing plan needs to be built around your
                        specific location and capacity goals, focusing on
                        high-conversion local channels rather than broad,
                        expensive campaigns.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA SECTION -->
    <section class="py-12 md:py-20">
        <Container size="md">
            <div
                class="glass-panel rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-10 text-center border-2 border-purple-200/50 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50/50 to-white/50"
            >
                <h2
                    class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 md:mb-4"
                >
                    See How Much YOU Could Make in Your State
                </h2>
                <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 mb-4 md:mb-6">
                    Get your personalized income estimate to understand your
                    revenue potential.
                </p>
                <a
                    href="/#calculator"
                    class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 text-white font-medium px-6 py-3 md:px-8 md:py-4 shadow-lg transition-all text-sm md:text-base"
                >
                    Use the Free Calculator →
                </a>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>
</Layout>
